text: ovun mata danduvama patita vu kalhi aho musa ! obage paramadhipati oba vetin pratigna gat ayurin oba apa venuven ohugen prarthana karanu mænava ! mema danduvama apa vetin oba ivat kara dunne nam niyata vasayenma api oba va visvasa karannemu. tavada oba samanga israil daruvan va yavannemu yæyi ovuhu pævasuvoya
